#Program: Create a grade calculator for the mean grade of three quizzes
#Author: Ashley Meredith Marks
#Creation Date: October 23rd, 2025
#Last modified: October 23rd, 2025

#User inputs their name
Name = input("Name: ")

#User inputs their grades for each of the three quizzes
quiz1 = int(input("Enter your grade for Quiz 1: "))
quiz2 = int(input("Enter your grade for Quiz 2: "))
quiz3 = int(input("Enter your grade for Quiz 3: "))

#Sums the quiz grades
quizsum = quiz1 + quiz2 + quiz3

#Calculate the average of the three grades, rounding to 2 decimal places
average = round((quizsum / 3), 2)
    

#Print out the message to inform the student of their quiz average
print(Name, "has a quiz average of:", average)

